        "collapsible_tab_4YyHJK": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "HOW DOES THIS WORK?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "content": "<p>If your child’s Evercalm Tee is worn out, damaged, or no longer fits, just get in touch and we’ll arrange a replacement. There are no limits and no complicated steps.</p><p>Evercalm was created for children with autism and sensory sensitivities who rely on clothing that feels familiar and predictable. When a t-shirt becomes part of a child’s routine, replacing it with something different can be difficult.</p><p>That’s why Evercalm is made to last. Each tee is crafted from soft, combed cotton and finished to keep the same feel and fit over time. The classic cut avoids tightness and cling, while the pre-shrunk fabric and reinforced stitching help it stay consistent through frequent wear and washing.</p><p>Our replacement promise exists so the routine does not have to change, even as your child grows. The t-shirt they trust can stay the t-shirt they wear.</p><p>A simple promise, designed to support calmer, more predictable days.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_3Brz6X": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT'S COVERED IN THE GUARANTEE",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "content": "<p>We’ll replace your Evercalm Tee if you notice any of the following through normal wear:</p><p>✅ Holes appearing in the fabric<br/><br/>✅ Colour fading or looking dull over time<br/><br/>✅ Stitching coming loose<br/><br/>✅ Collar or sleeves losing their shape<br/><br/>✅ Accidental damage, including stains</p><p>For accidental damage, we ask that replacements are limited to <strong>one per year</strong>. We think that’s fair, and we hope you do too.</p><p>✅ Deodorant stains are also covered<br/><br/>For these, we ask that replacements are limited to <strong>one per month</strong>.</p><p><strong>What's not covered?</strong></p><p>❌ Intentional damage</p><p>We understand we can’t always know how damage happens, so this policy is built on trust. Most families are simply trying to keep a routine working, and that’s who this promise is for. We trust people to be honest and to use it fairly.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_rr63KB": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "ABOUT THE TEE",
            "icon": "shirt",
            "content": "<p>Classic, relaxed fit with a comfortable crew neckline</p><p>Mid-weight 165g fabric that feels substantial without being heavy<br/><br/>Slightly longer body length for comfortable everyday wear<br/><br/>Made from 100% organic, combed ringspun cotton for a smooth, soft feel<br/><br/>Peel-away neck label to leave the neckline smooth and irritation-free</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_JXrb7D": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "DELIVERY & RETURNS",
            "icon": "box",
            "content": "<p>Orders placed by 2pm are shipped same day. If this falls on a weekend, it will be shipped the next working day. <br/><br/>Allow 1-3 working days for UK delivery.</p><p>Allow 7-8 working days for USA / ROW delivery</p><p>We offer a no quibble 28 day return policy. We just ask that the tee is in the same condition as we sent it.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_B4eDpp": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "SIZING",
            "icon": "ruler",
            "content": "<p>Our premium heavyweight t-shirt is carefully and ethically crafted from 100% combed cotton. </p><p>Fitting is true to size, but if it's not the right size, we offer a free no quibble 28 day return / exchange window.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
