    "rich_text_UfhrYx": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Xe87LQ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT MAKES THIS DIFFERENT FROM OTHER KIDS' TEES?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_xXxLaU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most kids’ t-shirts are designed for price or appearance. Evercalm is designed for consistency. It uses soft, organic combed cotton that feels the same wear after wear, a peel-away neck label that removes a common source of irritation, and a classic fit that avoids tightness and cling. </p><p>The fabric is mid-weight and pre-shrunk so it keeps its shape and feel after washing. Nothing is added unless it helps the t-shirt stay comfortable and predictable.</p>"
          }
        },
