          }
        },
        "column_FaR7aa": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>WHAT'S COVERED</strong>",
            "text": "<p>✅ Holes appearing in the fabric<br/>✅ Colour fading or looking dull over time<br/>✅ Stitching coming loose<br/>✅ Collar or sleeves losing their shape<br/>✅ Logo fading or peeling if you’ve chosen a branded tee<br/>✅ Accidental damage, including stains or deodorant marks</p><p>For accidental damage, we ask that replacements are limited to <strong>one per month</strong>. This helps us keep the promise fair and sustainable for everyone.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_EEtgnn": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "WHAT'S NOT COVERED",
            "text": "<p>❌ Intentional damage</p><p>We know we cannot always tell how damage happens, so this guarantee is built on trust. It exists to support families who rely on consistency and routine, and we trust people to use it honestly and fairly.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
