    "collapsible_content_NNPzfc": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_UqUbNX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the Evercalm replacement promise work?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Evercalm is designed to be worn regularly and relied on. If your child’s t-shirt becomes worn out, damaged, or no longer fits, you can contact us and we’ll arrange a replacement.</p><p>The idea is simple: when a t-shirt becomes part of a routine, changing it can be difficult. Our replacement promise exists so the fit and feel don’t have to change, even as your child grows.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_fmCMR3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why is Evercalm different from a standard kids’ t-shirt?",
            "icon": "price_tag",
            "row_content": "<p>Most kids’ t-shirts are designed for style or price. Evercalm is designed for consistency.</p><p>It uses soft, organic combed cotton, a peel-away neck label, and a classic fit that avoids tightness and cling. The fabric is mid-weight and pre-shrunk so it feels the same after washing. Nothing is added unless it serves a purpose.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WQJC9K": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What happens if my Evercalm Tee is worn out or damaged?",
            "icon": "recycle",
            "row_content": "<p>If your Evercalm Tee develops holes, loose stitching, fading, or loses its shape through normal wear, we’ll replace it.</p><p>Accidental damage and stains are also covered within our fair use policy. The goal is to support families who rely on consistency, while keeping the promise sustainable for everyone.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_67nEph": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Evercalm is designed to be worn again and again",
            "icon": "plant",
            "row_content": "<p>Evercalm is made to reduce the need for constant replacement and re-adjustment.</p><p>Children who find clothing comfortable often want to wear the same items repeatedly. Evercalm is built to withstand frequent wear and washing, and when it does need replacing, the next one is made to feel the same.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_g3tTQJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Evercalm comfortable for sensitive kids?",
            "icon": "shirt",
            "row_content": "<p>Comfort is not just about softness. It’s about predictability.</p><p>Evercalm removes common triggers like scratchy labels and changing fit. The peel-away neck label leaves the neckline smooth, the fabric stays consistent, and the cut avoids pressure points or cling.</p><p>Every detail is designed to reduce irritation and distraction.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_LbVnQH": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is there anything I should know about the guarantee?",
            "icon": "eye",
            "row_content": "<p>The Evercalm guarantee is built on trust.</p><p>It doesn’t cover intentional damage, and we ask families to follow our fair use guidelines for accidental replacements. The promise exists to support real, everyday use and to help maintain routines, not to be taken advantage of.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
